{"id": "1218547337404747787", "channel_id": "1218547337404747787", "type": 0, "author_id": "386730481502257153", "author_name": "yulina_aa", "author_bot": false, "content": "希洛大招寫抽出來的打擊不吃手牌上限，問題在臍帶作用下希洛不管吃幾個胚胎手牌上限還是12張 可以請程序排查一下嗎？", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T13:12:04.752000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1218547337404747787", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」希洛大招敘述問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1218478868910837761", "channel_id": "1218478868910837761", "type": 0, "author_id": "986926416098643980", "author_name": "wuriyuekong", "author_bot": false, "content": "既不算分、也（似乎）没有特殊的造物，有什么必要一遍遍打？\n我能想到的合理化的办法是：算分后另外掉落，或者加点游戏别的地方没有的造物/刻印等，这样可玩性高点。不然很无聊。", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T08:40:00.591000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1218478868910837761", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」活动不能扫荡的合理性…？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1218428845095522385", "channel_id": "1218428845095522385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1191620861699031083", "author_name": "dulce_lxy", "author_bot": false, "content": "现在体力上限180，活动关一次消耗120，满体力上线就只能打一把。然后就要等半天体力回到120才能再打一次，这也太难受了。能不能改成莉莉活动那种60*2的形式或者把体力上限改成240啊", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T05:21:13.984000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1218428845095522385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」关于活动关体力消耗的问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1218679966665801748", "channel_id": "1218679966665801748", "type": 0, "author_id": "731561666029944885", "author_name": "i__need__healing", "author_bot": false, "content": "這次新增的編隊功能蠻方便的，可以一次編輯多種隊伍。但是一但要打融災禁區，還是得要重新編排所有5組隊伍和命輪密契等，有時候想要查看已經使用過的命輪也不太方便。\n\n(如果不想要讓玩家直接套用現有編隊的隊伍，又或是官方可以考慮出一個單獨給融災禁區專用的編隊介面?)", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T21:59:06.032000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1218679966665801748", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」請問是否可以讓\"融災禁區\"能直接從\"編隊\"去套用現有隊伍設定?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1218428658713231380", "channel_id": "1218428658713231380", "type": 0, "author_id": "906415835810250812", "author_name": "cadejomordred", "author_bot": false, "content": "請問官方隊旺達的定位是甚麼?\n反擊隊的問題是血量跟不上敵人的輸出就沒有傷害\n但是旺達是超維界域 沒有血肉界域的百分比回血和提高死亡抵抗的手段\n身為防御角 盾不夠厚\n有疊反擊輸出的機制 但傷害不夠\n而大部分關卡都有回合數的成就條件\n是否考慮再調整一下角色\n如3點反擊增加傷害\n或增加盾的厚度和手段之類的", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T05:20:29.547000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1218428658713231380", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」旺達定位", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1218548131923492936", "channel_id": "1218548131923492936", "type": 0, "author_id": "1215520307519954984", "author_name": "qiyuan48", "author_bot": false, "content": "在特殊事件中选择两个以下白银造物后\n\n莱茵特草纸书 选择刻印高级刻章\n须臾的火 选择复制一张牌\n\n莱茵特草纸书的效果被须臾的火覆盖，没有进入选择高级刻章的界面而是直接进入了复制牌的界面", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T13:15:14.180000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1218548131923492936", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」活动图特殊事件bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
