{"id": "1218465334718369884", "channel_id": "1218465334718369884", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181568185347080212", "author_name": "xianle_25809", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一次没抽到想普池相应命令（角色），第二（三）次必然抽中。。普池命轮真的大海捞针", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T07:46:13.788000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1218465334718369884", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」能不能加入愿望功能，普池定向命轮，唤醒体", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1218656454504878230", "channel_id": "1218656454504878230", "type": 0, "author_id": "816680047766274129", "author_name": "luoin2435", "author_bot": false, "content": "剛剛打融災的時候發現，開大後獲得的“巨刃之威”被水母2費棄掉之後，後來抽上來就變0費了，文案寫的是保留在手上的話算力消耗-1，那它在牌庫裡也減算力消耗應該是bug", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T20:25:40.296000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "💔", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1218656454504878230", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」戈利亞bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
